e in world sprinting.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"one-hundredth\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest race\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"world sprinting\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the fastest event of its type in history.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fastest event\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"its type\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shout-out also to teenagers Nkoana and Walaza.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shout-out\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"teenagers\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"Nkoana\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"Walaza\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latter chose to forego exams to compete for his country in Paris.\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1313023131559917e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latter\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"exams\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"23-year-old Shaun Maswanganyi also has a massive future in sprinting.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_Maswanganyi\", \"score\": 0.9999968692872139, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaun Maswanganyi\", \